      "id": "PopularPost290833",
      "post_content": "A weakness of this card is that if you want higher damage you need more targets. It's far more effective against a creature deck than a control deck, thus limited its application.  \n  \nThat said, I'd only use Firestorm where discarding is beneficial, such as hellbent, madness, or with phoenixes, for creature killing there are less restrictive options.",
