    {
      "id": "PopularPost142356",
      "post_content": "@ Draugnor: No, you can't target anything more than once. The key operator here is \"each of X targets\". It would be broken beyond belief if it could hit a single target multiple times.\n  \n   \nTurn one: Play mountain. Cast Firestorm, discarding five cards; you deal your opponent five damage five times.\n  \n   \nIt would be a one-mana, one-card instant victory.",
      "posted_by": "scumbling1",
